<lyrics>[V1]
 1- yasūʿu rabĩy ạảḥabã ạl̊kẖuṭāh̊
 man̊ yā turay̱ mitẖ̊lu hadẖā ạl̊ḥabīb̊
 min̊ ạảj̊lihim̊ qad̊ jāʾa min̊ ʿulạh̊
 man̊ yā turay̱ mitẖ̊lu hadẖā ạl̊ḥabīb̊

[V2]
 2- min̊ ạảj̊lihim̊ dẖāqa maẘta ạlṣãlīb̊
 man̊ gẖaẙruhu fī ạtĩḍāʿiⁿ ʿajīb̊
 maḍay̱ līaḥ̊mila ạl̊ḥuk̊ma ạlrãhīb̊
 man̊ yā turay̱ mitẖ̊lu hadẖā ạl̊ḥabīb̊

[V3]
 3- fah̊wa ạlãdẖī luṭ̊fuhu ʿamãnā
 man̊ yā turay̱ mitẖ̊lu hadẖā ạl̊ḥabīb̊
 fākẖ̊tāra ạản̊ yaf̊tadī jin̊sanā
 man̊ yā turay̱ mitẖ̊lu hadẖā ạl̊ḥabīb̊

[V4]
 4- ʿanãạ ʿafā gẖāfiraⁿạ dẖan̊banā
 fādī ạl̊waray̱ dẖākiraⁿạ ạảṣ̊lanā
 waḥajaba ạlṭãr̊fa ʿan̊ jah̊linā
 man̊ yā turay̱ mitẖ̊lu hadẖā ạl̊ḥabīb̊</lyrics>
<title>yswʿ rby ạ̉ḥb ạlkẖṭạẗ</title>
</song>